### Test: Service Unavailable (503) - Circuit Breaker Open
### This test validates that when the circuit breaker is open, requests return 503
### Note: This requires circuit breaker to be triggered (e.g., provider consistently failing)

POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/validate-address
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "123 Main St, Springfield, IL 62701"
}

### Expected Response (503 Service Unavailable):
### {
###   "statusCode": 503,
###   "message": "Service temporarily unavailable",
###   "error": "Service Unavailable"
### }

